	KEY ALT+E, ""
ON PAD _742109ywd OF _MSYSMENU ACTIVATE POPUP salir
ON PAD _742109ywe OF _MSYSMENU ACTIVATE POPUP configurac
ON PAD _742109ywf OF _MSYSMENU ACTIVATE POPUP tablasvari
